        <Summary>KDE4 utilities</Summary>
        <Description>Contains base KDE4 utilities. In package ark (archive manager), kcalc (scientific calculator), kgpg (cryptographic key manager), superkaramba (plasmoid-like widgets on desktop) and kwalletmanager (password manager) applications are included.</Description>
